Dear Sir or Madam,



We want to capture data from Shimmer3 sensor in a GNU/Linux machine; therefore we follow the instruction in the section of ShimmerCapture on Linux.



I have to say that pairing the USB bluetooth connection is not a problem; however, I am wondering if you have an application that I can run on a GNU/Linux machine.



From the applications available at [1], you only provide executable applications for windows (ShimmerCapture v0.5_Linux.exe).



